        "subject": "LU-10459 lnd: throttle tx based on queue depth",
        "message": "LU-10459 lnd: throttle tx based on queue depth\n\nThrottle the transmits based on the negotiated conn queue depth\nto ensure we keep the number of outstanding transmits below the\nnegotiated queue depth.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/30751\nLustre-commit: e86f55798ca7bc8f7fe22dd48c9d9f52c1bb029a\n\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <amir.shehata@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I27190364904d6c79c0cd6d382228f8b8d2b11ba0\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@yahoo.com>\nReviewed-by: Dmitry Eremin <dmitry.eremin@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <mdiep@whamcloud.com>\n"
